  <div id="article-header">
    
    
      <h1 class="title">
      A comunicação de intelectuais, ativistas e veículos baianos no FSM 
  </h1>
  <span class="publishing-info">
  <span class="date">
    Marzo 20, 2018 1:58
  </span>
  <span class="author">
    , by <a href="http://softwarelivre.org/bahia1798">Luiz Gonzaga das Virgens</a>
  </span>
  <span class="comments">
     - <a href="/bahia-1798/conteudos/noticias-da-home/a-comunicacao-de-intelectuais-ativistas-e-veiculos-baianos-no-fsm#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a>
